* every command should run on mongo client 

* Commands
1. to see all the databases
>> show dbs

2. create database/ use any database
>> use database_name    use service_db

3. to see the collection in database
>> show collections

4. to create collection
>> db.info.insert({"dependencies": {"chalk": "^5.0.1","cors": "^2.8.5","dotenv": "^16.0.1","express": "^4.18.1","mongodb": "^4.7.0","morgan": "^1.10.0"})

5. to see data from the collection
>> db user find()


